---
import '../styles/global.css';
const phoneDisplay = "55 6323 2833";
const phoneLink = "+525563232833";
const doctorName = "Dr. Vicente Lavielle";
const specialty = "Pediatra";
const location = "Cuautitlán Izcalli";
const yearsExperience = "30+";
const cedula = "1707043";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <!-- Google Tag Manager -->
    <script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
    new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
    j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
    'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
    })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-TB2P8V8P');</script>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager -->

    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <meta name="description" content={`${doctorName} - Pediatra en ${location} con más de ${yearsExperience} años de experiencia. Llama para agendar una cita.`} />
    <title>{doctorName} - Pediatra en {location}</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 antialiased">
    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-TB2P8V8P"
    height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->

    <main class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-xl w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8 md:p-12">
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">
            {specialty} en {location}
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
		  {doctorName} Sotomayor
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            Más de {yearsExperience} años cuidando la salud de tus hijos
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8 pb-8 border-b border-slate-200">
          <span>Cédula profesional {cedula}</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>Egresado de la UNAM</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>20+ opiniones verificadas</span>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Agenda tu cita llamando directamente al consultorio:
          </p>
          <a
            href={`tel:${phoneLink}`}
            onclick="dataLayer && dataLayer.push({event: 'phone_click'});"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full md:w-auto bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 active:bg-blue-800 text-white text-xl font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-md transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M6.62 10.79a15.05 15.05 0 006.59 6.59l2.2-2.2a1 1 0 011.01-.24 11.36 11.36 0 003.58.57 1 1 0 011 1V20a1 1 0 01-1 1A17 17 0 013 4a1 1 0 011-1h3.5a1 1 0 011 1 11.36 11.36 0 00.57 3.58 1 1 0 01-.25 1.01l-2.2 2.2z"/>
            </svg>
            {phoneDisplay}
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-3">
            Horario de atención: lunes a sábado, 8:00 a 14:30
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="mb-3">
            Con más de tres décadas de experiencia clínica, el Dr. Lavielle ofrece
            atención pediátrica integral desde el nacimiento hasta la adolescencia.
          </p>
          <p>
            Consultas en Hospital San Rafael {location}.
            Se aceptan GNP Seguros, MetLife y Seguros Monterrey.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>